Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:54.06,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189890,1194060}Sanjou. Did you ever think about the team during the game?{NOTE:三条。お前はあの間中、チームの事を考えたこともあったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.90,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194060,1194900}Well?{NOTE:どうだ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:59.24,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194900,1199240}You were focused on competing for points with Ayuhara.{NOTE:お前は鮎原と競い合って、ポイントを稼ぐことで懸命だったはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:03.91,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199240,1203910}But getting as many points as possible leads to team victory.{NOTE:でも、でもポイントを少しでも多く上げることがチームの勝利に繋がります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.32,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203910,1205320}Am I wrong?{NOTE:そうじゃないですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:06.53,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205320,1206530}No, you're right.{NOTE:その通りだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:09.16,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206530,1209160}However, it worked only for a single set.{NOTE:ただし、ワンセットだけのゲームならばのことだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:10.37,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209160,1210370}Only one set?{NOTE:ワンセットだけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:16.46,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212580,1216460}In the first set of today's game, your attacks, competing with each other…{NOTE:今日の試合ワンセット目は競い合って打つアタックが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.50,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216460,1218500}…turned out to be tactical success.{NOTE:…戦術的にも成功した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.30,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219300,1223300}They couldn't predict which one of you would strike.{NOTE:相手はどちらが打つか予測がつかず、XXした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:29.43,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226010,1229430}In other words, you managed to briefly confuse them.{NOTE:つまり、めちゃくちゃぶりに目がくらんだと言うわけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.68,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229430,1230680}Confuse?{NOTE:めちゃくちゃ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:32.64,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230680,1232640}That's why you won the first set.{NOTE:それでワンセットは取ったが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.40,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232640,1237400}But they quickly saw through your messed up attacks.{NOTE:…相手チームはこの攻撃がめちゃくちゃなことを見抜いたのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:40.90,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237400,1240900}That's right. The tables have turned in the second set.{NOTE:そうだわ。二セット目からしぶとく拾ってきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.86,0:20:47.16,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244860,1247160}Your opponents stuck to team play.{NOTE:相手はチームプレーで粘った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.29,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247870,1250290}And so they gained a lead in the second set.{NOTE:それで、二セット目がリードされてしまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.29,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250290,1252290}But we won in the end.{NOTE:でも結局は勝ちました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:56.54,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252290,1256540}That's because Ayuhara abandoned the game against you.{NOTE:その原動力になったのは鮎原がお前との勝負を捨てたからだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.50,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256540,1258500}Huh? I-It can't be.{NOTE:え？そ、そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260130,1261880}So the coach has seen it after all.{NOTE:やっぱりコーチが見ていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261880,1263840}My decision at that time.{NOTE:あの時の決心よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263840,1266010}When they gained a lead on us in the second set.{NOTE:二セット目、リードされた後。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.43,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269970,1271430}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271430,1272480}Got it!{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:16.60,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272850,1276600}At that time I had completely forgotten that I was an attacker.{NOTE:あの時は私は自分がアタッカーXXすっかり忘れてしまっていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:23.90,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278150,1283900}Saying it was teamwork just because she was thinking on her feet is a bit of a stretch.{NOTE:でも、咄嗟の行動を取っただけで、チームワークができたなんて…こじつけもいいところだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:24.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283900,1284950}That wasn't it.{NOTE:違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:28.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284950,1288870}That wasn't it! I remembered volleyball basics back then.{NOTE:違うわ！私はあの時バレーの基本をもう一度知らされたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288870,1290870}And that is teamwork.{NOTE:チームワークを。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.75,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290870,1293750}That's right. And yet, Sanjou-san…{NOTE:その通りよ。なのに、三条さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:37.08,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1293750,1297080}– …you ignored team play until the end.\N– Exactly.{NOTE:—最後までチームプレーを無視したんだ。\\N—そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:41.21,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297080,1301210}No matter how good you are, you can't win a volleyball game by yourself.{NOTE:いくら個人の力が優れていても、バレーは一人では勝てないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.88,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301210,1302880}Are you finished?{NOTE:抗議はそれだけ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.97,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302880,1304970}No, I'm not. One more thing.{NOTE:それだけではない。もう一つがあるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.39,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304970,1308390}It was Ayuhara-san's power that saved us in the second set.{NOTE:二セット目から見事に盛り返したは鮎原さんの力だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309090,1310930}I was like in a trance.{NOTE:でも、無我夢中だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:58.90,Alternative,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317560,1318900}Leave it to me.{NOTE:任しておけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.52,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319520,1321520}She received it in a way I couldn't ever do.{NOTE:自分でも思いがけないレシーブだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:02.82,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321520,1322820}Are you okay?{NOTE:大丈夫？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:08.28,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326240,1328280}Just three points left! Fight!{NOTE:さ、あと三点よ。ファイト！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.16,Alternative,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1328280,1329160}Yeah!{NOTE:おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:11.99,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330160,1331990}That… that was teamwork.{NOTE:あれが…あらげチームワーク。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.62,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331990,1333620}That is volleyball!{NOTE:あれがバレーなんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:18.67,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333620,1338670}While Sanjou-san thought only of herself, Ayuhara-san already played like a captain.{NOTE:三条さんはXXXあの時既に鮎原さんはキャプテンの役目を演じてたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.42,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338670,1341420}Yeah, she totally had that captain vibe.{NOTE:そうよ。立派なキャプテンやったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:23.46,Default,Yoshimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341420,1343460}Our new captain.{NOTE:私達の新キャプテン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:24.88,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343460,1344880}Captain, banzai!{NOTE:キャプテン万歳。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:26.88,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1344880,1346880}Thank you. I'll work hard!{NOTE:ありがとう、頑張るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:29.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347680,1349130}I won.{NOTE:私は勝った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:30.72,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1349130,1350720}In the end, I won…{NOTE:やっぱり勝ったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:32.72,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350720,1352720}My love for volleyball prevailed.{NOTE:バレーを心から愛する私が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:34.22,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352720,1354220}Hahaha.{NOTE:はははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:41.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360560,1361810}Sanjou-san.{NOTE:三条さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:43.52,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361810,1363520}Heh, what a farce.{NOTE:ふん。滑稽だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:44.82,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363520,1364820}This is good.{NOTE:(XX・傑作)よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:45.78,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364820,1365780}Sanjou!{NOTE:三条！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:52.95,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1368570,1372950}What? Look at you coming up with these beautiful stories, thinking I don't know.{NOTE:何よ？知らないと思って、綺麗な理屈を並べて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:57.04,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372950,1377040}Wasn't Ayuhara Kozue already determined to become captain?{NOTE:どうせ、一番キャプテンは鮎原こずえって決まってたんじゃないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:58.87,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377040,1378870}What do you mean?{NOTE:な、何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:02.88,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1378870,1382880}Ayuhara-san, you're pretty good at seducing people.{NOTE:鮎原さんって人の心を掴むのがとても上手だって言ってるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382880,1384750}Sanjou-san!{NOTE:あ、三条さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.51,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1384750,1387510}– What the hell, Sanjou-san!\N– You stay out of this!{NOTE:—三条さん、何て事？\\N—後は黙って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.13,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387510,1389130}I know about everything.{NOTE:私は知ってるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:13.22,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389130,1393220}About how our coach has feelings for Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:コーチが鮎原さんに個人的な感情を持ってるって言うことはね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:15.26,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393220,1395260}Sanjou.{NOTE:三条。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:18.39,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1395260,1398390}To put it clearly, he's in love with her.{NOTE:つもり、はっきり言えば、好きだってことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:21.31,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1398390,1401310}Hahaha. What a comedy.{NOTE:はははは。滑稽だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:23.31,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401310,1403310}How filthy.{NOTE:不潔よ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405940,1407940}W-What the heck?{NOTE:な、何と事！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:29.11,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407940,1409110}Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.28,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1409110,1411280}– Kozue!\N– No! Let go of me!{NOTE:—こずえ！\\N—辞めて！放してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:34.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411280,1414070}I won't forgive such accusations.{NOTE:だって、だってあんな言いがかりに許さないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:35.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414070,1415160}That's just too low.{NOTE:汚すぎるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415160,1416580}Kozue, calm down.{NOTE:こずえ、落ち着いて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:39.16,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416580,1419160}That's right, captain. Stay calm.{NOTE:そうよ、キャプテン。冷静に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:44.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1422670,1424130}Coach!{NOTE:コーチ！}
